# Default Kamal secrets file.
#
# The main app requires explicit deployment destinations, so its deploys use:
#
#   bin/kamal deploy -d staging
#   bin/kamal deploy -d production
#
# Those read .kamal/secrets-common plus .kamal/secrets.staging/.production.
#
# The destination-less standalone imgproxy deploy:
#
#   bin/kamal deploy -c config/deploy.imgproxy.yml
#
# reads this file plus .kamal/secrets-common, where the shared IMGPROXY_KEY and
# IMGPROXY_SALT live. Nothing destination-specific is needed here.
